msgid "WP Job Portal is a simple yet powerful job board plugin with a step-by-step YouTube guide to ensure ease of use."
msgstr "WP Job Portal adalah plugin papan lowongan yang sederhana namun kuat, dengan panduan YouTube langkah demi langkah agar mudah digunakan."

msgid "WP Job Portal Login Page"
msgstr "Halaman login WP Job Portal"

msgid "WP Job Portal offer a feature for Employer and Job Seekers , which allows them to take PDF of Resume and can save it."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja dan pencari kerja untuk membuat PDF CV dan menyimpannya."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a message feature for Employers and Job Seekers. All the Employers and Job Seekers can message each other."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur pesan untuk Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja. Semua Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja dapat saling berkirim pesan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for admin to add multiple credit system against particular actions. Admin can add multiple packages against particular actions."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi admin untuk menambahkan beberapa sistem kredit untuk tindakan tertentu. Admin dapat menambahkan beberapa paket untuk tindakan tertentu."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for an employer to copy their jobs. Employers can copy their jobs easily."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja untuk menyalin lowongan mereka dengan mudah."

msgid "WP job Portal offers a feature for employers to add multi companies. Employers will add their desired multi-companies."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja untuk menambahkan beberapa perusahaan sesuai kebutuhan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for Employers to add multi-departments related to jobs. Job seeker can apply to jobs related to the desired department."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja untuk menambahkan beberapa departemen yang terkait dengan lowongan. Pencari kerja dapat melamar lowongan sesuai departemen yang diinginkan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to make folders. Employers can make a folder and copy their resumes into the folders."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja untuk membuat folder dan menyalin CV ke dalam folder tersebut."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for employers to perform some actions on resumes. Employers have some rights to reject or accept the job seeker resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pemberi kerja untuk melakukan tindakan pada CV. Pemberi kerja dapat menerima atau menolak CV pencari kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for making the jobs as Featured Job. This will help to make it easier for job seekers to find jobs."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur untuk menjadikan lowongan sebagai Lowongan Unggulan. Ini membantu pencari kerja menemukan lowongan dengan lebih mudah."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for searching the jobs by tags. Employers will add some tags related to jobs search."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur pencarian lowongan berdasarkan tag. Pemberi kerja dapat menambahkan tag yang terkait dengan pencarian lowongan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for the job seeker to add their multi-resume. Job seeker will be able to create a multiple resume for applying any job."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur bagi pencari kerja untuk menambahkan beberapa CV, sehingga mereka dapat membuat beberapa CV untuk melamar lowongan yang berbeda."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for users to see address data for states, cities or both. Admin will upload that file."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur agar pengguna dapat melihat data alamat untuk provinsi, kota, atau keduanya. Admin akan mengunggah file tersebut."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature for visitors. A visitor can apply to any company posted jobs. The visitor will apply for the jobs by their resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur untuk pengunjung. Pengunjung dapat melamar lowongan yang diposting perusahaan menggunakan CV mereka."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a feature in which Employer and Job Seekers can share and tell their friends about Jobs by sending them an email."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur agar Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja dapat membagikan lowongan kepada teman melalui email."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a jobs share feature on various social media sites for Employers and Job Seekers."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur berbagi lowongan di berbagai situs media sosial untuk Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers a Resume and print feature. Employer and Job Seeker can view the Resume page or take a print of the Resume."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur CV dan cetak. Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja dapat melihat halaman CV atau mencetak CV."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers an outstanding feature for employers to featured their companies. Employers will be able to featured their desired companies."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan fitur unggulan bagi pemberi kerja untuk menampilkan perusahaan mereka sebagai perusahaan unggulan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers multiple reports by jobs, by companies and by resume. Admin can see overall reports of Employer and Job Seeker."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan beberapa laporan berdasarkan lowongan, perusahaan, dan CV. Admin dapat melihat laporan keseluruhan Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers Real Simple Syndication (RSS) to set feeds for the jobs. Admin manipulates RSS settings. Employers and Job Seekers can see the Jobs RSS."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan Real Simple Syndication (RSS) untuk mengatur feed lowongan. Admin mengelola pengaturan RSS. Pemberi Kerja dan Pencari Kerja dapat melihat RSS Lowongan."

msgid "WP Job Portal offers timely customer support. If you have any queries, we're here to help you every step of the way."
msgstr "WP Job Portal menawarkan dukungan pelanggan yang responsif. Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, kami siap membantu di setiap langkah."

